column5: Hey all, just in case anyone is interested, CNN is doing a report on a young Autistic girl....don't know much about it at this point...I will after I watch it  I recieved this e-mail today  "Hello All--Some of you may already be aware that Dr. Sanjay Gupta, chief medical correspondent for CNN, will be hosting a special programme on autism this coming Monday night, Nov. 19th at 10 PM on CNN. It should be interesting."  Just thought I'd let you know  Maureen
I just told my wife about it, as her cousin is dealing with a child with autism, it wasn't on. Did we miss it?     Just heard it is on next. Thank you!
No, it was on, it was the third story I think?  Very interesting indeed.  I fell asleep before it was over  but here is the link from CNN...check out her video's if you're on high speed.  Maureen
